<h1>Appearance</h1>


  
  <p>Looking your best at an interview is very important. Your appearance at an interview is your potential employer's first impression of you. By presenting a profession and clean appearance, you can ingrain a sense of confidence in your ability to complete the the tasks that your employer is looking for. The following suggestions of attire can serve you as potential guidelines:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <div class="list-tips">
    <li>Clean, polished, and conservative dress shoes</li>
    <li>Well-groomed hairstyle</li>
    <li>Cleaned and trimmed fingernails</li>
    <li>Minimal cologne or perfume</li>
    <li>Minimal jewelry</li>
  </div>
  </ul>
  
